name: Family Is Whatever
description: We get to define what family looks like for us. We get to choose who we are close to and who we share space with. We get to be surrounded by love and support. This piece is dedicated to everyone who has had to forge chosen family and who is ever so grateful for it. Limited edition of 10 by Edgar Fabián Frías / @edgarfabianfrias | 1080 x 1080 | .mp4 | 2021
